Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政治庇護?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈的軍師要逃亡到我國來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多倫卡喀的瘋狂野心已經無法抑止了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去,整個蓋亞都將面臨前所未有的災難?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就陣前倒戈了是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敵人隨便說什麼都信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們還搞什麼政治啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實讓人不太敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我並非空手而來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴風雨的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯的投靠\N讓事情有了重大轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於寨巴哈的危機感終於成為了現實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞與周邊國家結為軍事同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然阿斯多利亞為了得到寨巴哈的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以接納了弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但梵卻還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你光在皇宮內的避難所幫忙還覺得不夠嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為城裏會被破壞成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有部分的責任在我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不會自己一個人來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒找你一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吵架嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞煩各位光臨這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下真是惶恐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是希望能給予遭逢苦難的人們些許鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要推擠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有足夠的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做這些事的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈說不定會趁機攻打過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你滿腦子都是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不主動出擊就只能等著被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的職業軍人是嗎?你難道就沒有別的想法了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈會毀滅蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟它毀滅法尼利亞一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就請你多加油吧!法尼利亞王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有玩具?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先…先等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,別亂拉我尾巴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然跟大家玩在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她能體會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子們都失去了親人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟她一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭或許只會讓那樣的孩子不斷增加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你小時候都跟弗肯玩些什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那與這無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有事情忙,總不好我一個人無所事事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還跑出皇宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不明白自己對蓋亞有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是不說一聲就到處亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟梵一起去法尼利亞的時候也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…我覺得那件事跟亞連無關
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事不要瞞著我好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有瞞著你什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等一下會自己回宮裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然那麼不耐煩還對亞連說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想家了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?梵他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望能藉此讓你們合好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真是一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒辦法讓他瞭解呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會害怕嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是曾派出幸運強化兵企圖要將你捉走的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是完全不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過．
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我害怕的話,你也會跟著起戒心,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得先去信賴對方纔能取得對方的信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會要求阿斯多利亞的庇護
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定也是有目的的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你還是能感受到,我對你的信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能沒辦法全部傳達給你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這就是你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾格薩迪亞軍「特力夫號」抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉斯來的先遣部隊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定將於明天早晨抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄達勒斯軍、西薩利歐軍,連巴斯蘭都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這會是場蓋亞有史以來的大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到出兵的命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明時,我跟梵就得出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要告訴你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特公國的西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蜜拉娜公主的王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪蓮妮公主與我曾墜入不倫戀情的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子是我與瑪蓮妮公主的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的內心無法允許我繼續瞞著你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在曉得這一切之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還願意愛我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:10:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生生世世在不變的天空與月光下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮游要塞迪雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪雷特?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歇士達在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達雷特呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比歐雷呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說死了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是賈久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是迪蘭度大人的士兵,您睢一的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睢一的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那架新的人型裝甲\N準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好久沒上戰場了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,原來你在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你談談小瞳的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我向她求婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答覆就等到回來之後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心中就會不可思議地感到平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就好好保護她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會把她讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要我犧牲性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子是亞連的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會不會回不了地球了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我這身打扮如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,您怎麼能做這些事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是洗洗衣服罷了,德萊甸不會有意見的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說對吧,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想跟你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意聽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想跟我商量什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這是我朋友發生的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有個交往中的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個人其實是個花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後她還發現對方已經有個私生子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個人其實是個花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且竟然還有私生子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你早就知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人活在世上就會遇到種種遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在認識前就發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能認命接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜,你到現在還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,可以看到藍潘德了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇歐,要優雅地著陸喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們可是阿斯多利亞的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫守備隊跟裝甲隊出動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫裝甲隊出動…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港□燒起來了,士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈發動偷襲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯,直接衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要駕駛謝拉撒特出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備放謝拉撒特下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量降低高度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇歐,衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去轉移敵人的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候,我究竟該相信什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該相信誰好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全陷入一片火海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右翼,快去守住右翼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕農的人型裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三小隊到前面去快到前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會在這種地方見面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的人型裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了,我們來玩一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒光光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看,這樣會燙傷的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連·歇薩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭你!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,繞到我的後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是傳說的伊斯帕農的人型裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒他就能立大功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一樣強嘛,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太多事了,賈久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏得了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會看見呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手,別再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,不要…不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股異常的殺氣是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我愈來愈興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會死在你手上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡,賈久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全掉進了對方的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快回去帕拉斯才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家為什麼要打個不停呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎,藍潘德全毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同盟軍的正式會議只好在帕拉斯舉行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只好這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈那些人是來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定要提早做準備才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至要考慮先發制人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不先出手的話反倒會被對方給幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你滿腦子就只想著要打仗呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場仗全是為了保護大家\N為了保護你而打的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本是在亨受打鬥的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不需要你用那種方式來保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也受夠了這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰快來讓我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我回到我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳\N小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您喜歡小瞳,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在呼喚著我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:57.34,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:05.79,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:13.42,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:19.57,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:21.93,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:26.94,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:30.78,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:34.58,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:38.59,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:42.09,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:49.56,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:57.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:05.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:13.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:19.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:21.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:26.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:30.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:34.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:38.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:42.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:49.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

